ygData.subject: Levels and Group
ygData.msgSnippet: Arghhhh The fastest way to level is to group - however, I keep having to make friends over and over.  I only play one or two hours a night five nights a week.
ygData.messageBody:
Arghhhh

The fastest way to level is to group - however, I keep having to make
friends over and over. I only play one or two hours a night five nights a
week. I appears everyone around my rank (16th, almost 17 I hope) must play
24/7! One day they are 16, the next time I log on they are 22! Oh well,
such is life.

Guess I will have to start over on the new server as a puny Gnome Wizard or
a Tree Hugging Wood Elf Druid. Just kidding, there is still no better life
that being a barbarian warrior. Just venting.

For the Honor and Glory of Rallos Zek;

Patty of Halas
username: Patricia
